column5: i got out before the season closed for some last ice action, the fish are very predictable at this time of year and are not shy when they hit, oversized williams was the key i hope you enjoy the video
Wel done. Those were some beauty walleye.
Sweet footage.  I can't wait until I can fish in my tee shirt haha
Nice mixed bag of fish. I love the Williams to.  Thanks for sharing
Great footage and video.  T-shirt, daylight walleye and all alone on the ice.... doesnt get better than that!!!
awesome day on the ice, Big Fish !   looks like you got a nice sunburn after all...   great video...
Nice video!  Thanx for sharing.  Ice fishing in a T shirt.  Gotta love it.
